==Game Description======================================================

In Minecraft: Story Mode, playing as either a male or female hero named 'Jesse,' you'll embark on a perilous adventure across the Overworld, through the Nether, to the End, and beyond.
 
http://store.steampowered.com/app/376870/

==Installation==========================================================

1. Unrar.
2. Burn or mount the image.
3. Install the game. 
4. Copy over the cracked content from the /Crack directory on the image to your game install directory.
5. Play the game.
6. Support the software developers. If you like this game, BUY IT!
